text: Thomas Hepburn (20 December 1839 - 22 April 1921) was an Australian cricketer. He played two first-class cricket matches for Victoria between 1872 and 1873. ==See also== * List of Victoria first-class cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1839 births Category:1921 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:Victoria cricketers Category:Cricketers from Melbourne
